name your price.

22
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:24,199
10,000 taels of gold.

23
00:03:24,719 --> 00:03:25,240
Outrageous!

24
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,879
That's exorbitant!

25
00:03:31,639 --> 00:03:32,639
10,000 taels of gold?

26
00:03:34,439 --> 00:03:35,080
In Dali,

27
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:38,719
it's the annual military budget.

28
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,120
Mr. Duan,

29
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:41,759
you decide.

30
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,759
Is the Nine Yin True Sutra

31
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:45,439
worth this price?

32
00:03:51,759 --> 00:03:52,680
How about this?

33
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,680
Since you're a regular client,

34
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,400
I won't push you.

35
00:03:56,919 --> 00:03:57,840
I'll first tell you

36
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,599
half the info.

37
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,280
You think about it.

38
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,039
Tomorrow,

39
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:03,560
tell me your answer.

40
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,319
Speak.

41
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,400
The Living Map

42
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,479
is currently with Ouyang Feng,

43
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:14,080
in Mount Baituo.

44
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,680
Ouyang Feng?

45
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:18,399
Isn't he with Huang Yaoshi?

46
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,600
They have some connection.

47
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,560
If they made some arrangement,

48
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:24,800
even Mr. Know-It-All wouldn't know.

49
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,040
Mr. Duan,

50
00:04:28,199 --> 00:04:29,800
the information is confirmed.

51
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,319
If it's false,

52
00:04:31,839 --> 00:04:32,439
I will

53
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,120
return your gold tenfold.

54
00:04:35,439 --> 00:04:36,519
He considers you a friend.

55
00:04:36,639 --> 00:04:37,439
He saved you.

56
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,000
Yet you sicced snakes on him?

57
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,120
The Sutra's

58
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,040
on Mount Hua,

59
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:43,879
but it's vast.

60
00:04:44,199 --> 00:04:44,879
I won't tell you

61
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:45,680
how to find it.

62
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:17,439
Here.

63
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,199
You're despicable.

64
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,240
Who knows if you

65
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:20,800
poisoned this?

66
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,839
Any family left?

67
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:39,680
None.

68
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:41,879
All dead.

69
00:05:46,199 --> 00:05:46,959
How?

70
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,040
Storytellers say

71
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,759
there are many martial artists.

72
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:54,279
They learn skills,

73
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,680
defend justice,

74
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:57,240
and help the weak.

75
00:05:58,399 --> 00:05:59,680
But given what I've witnessed,

76
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,759
you martial artists

77
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:05,079
never protect commoners.

78
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,879
Instead, you kill

79
00:06:08,399 --> 00:06:09,560
and plunder for the Sutra.

80
00:06:11,319 --> 00:06:12,519
You even betray kin.

81
00:06:14,399 --> 00:06:15,920
My parents were killed

82
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:20,079
by villains

83
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:20,759
like you.

84
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,079
Storytellers' tales

85
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:34,160
are fictional.

86
00:06:34,879 --> 00:06:35,720
All lies.

87
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:38,519
So, you admit it?

88
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:40,639
Admit what?

89
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,800
You're evil.

90
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:46,560
Right.

91
00:06:47,759 --> 00:06:48,600
I'm evil.

92
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:51,600
I'm Ouyang Feng, a villain.

93
00:06:52,879 --> 00:06:53,519
But your parents

94
00:06:53,519 --> 00:06:54,680
weren't killed by me.

95
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,800
You killed them.

96
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,199
Nonsense!

97
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:01,079
Your weakness doomed them.

98
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:02,600
You couldn't protect anyone.

99
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:03,879
You had to watch

100
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,439
helplessly as they died before you,

101
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,920
with no strength to resist,

102
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,199
nor means for vengeance.

103
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,560
I already took revenge.

104
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,920
The two guys who killed them

105
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,040
are dead now.

106
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,439
Did you kill them personally?

107
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,360
Yaoshi helped you kill them, right?

108
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,600
That's no real vengeance.

109
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:25,000
They killed your parents

110
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,120
because they had high martial skills.

111
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,000
Yaoshi could kill your foes

112
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:31,120
because he has higher martial skills.

113
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:33,160
Strength and power

114
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,560
are the ultimate truth in this world.

115
00:07:36,319 --> 00:07:37,480
The path to mastering it

116
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,319
lies in your grasp.

117
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,839
My patience with you wears thin.

118
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,439
Where is the Sutra hidden?

119
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,240
Tell me how to find it.

120
00:07:56,879 --> 00:07:58,199
Speak now, or I'll kill you.

121
00:07:58,879 --> 00:08:00,360
Huang Yaoshi is powerful.

122
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,040
He'll surely find us soon.

123
00:08:02,399 --> 00:08:03,399
He still needs me

124
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:05,199
to save his wife's life.

125
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,439
Kill me,

126
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,720
and you'll kill his wife.

127
00:08:07,759 --> 00:08:08,600
He'll hunt you

128
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:09,759
till he dies.

129
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:12,519
The Sutra isn't a medical book.

130
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,600
It can't save lives.

131
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:15,720
Enough of your schemes.

132
00:08:15,879 --> 00:08:16,680
He mentioned

133
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,319
a Healing Chapter in it.

134
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:20,000
He wants to save his wife,

135
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:21,720
so he'll come here soon.

136
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:23,120
You'll meet your end today.

137
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:29,079
Move.

138
00:08:30,279 --> 00:08:31,279
Let go!

139
00:08:37,639 --> 00:08:38,039
Mr. Duan.

140
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,559
That unscrupulous guy

141
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:40,399
asks too much.

142
00:08:40,639 --> 00:08:41,519
Let's capture him

143
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,799
and press him.

144
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:45,159
In the martial world,

145
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,840
we should follow the rules.

146
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,000
Mr. Duan,

147
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:49,679
we can afford

148
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:50,600
the information,

149
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:51,440
but...

150
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:51,960
I know

151
00:08:52,559 --> 00:08:53,519
Dali is a narrow land,

152
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,159
not destitute nor wealthy

153
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:56,840
in resources.

154
00:08:58,279 --> 00:08:58,919
Well,

155
00:08:59,039 --> 00:09:00,200
it's no small sum.

156
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,080
Mr. Duan,

157
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,480
you must decide quickly.

158
00:09:02,799 --> 00:09:03,639
If you want the info,

159
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:04,759
don't hesitate.

160
00:09:07,279 --> 00:09:07,480
Well,

161
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,159
what about Gao Ang?

162
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:10,440
Sir.

163
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:15,879
Gao Ang,

164
00:09:17,039 --> 00:09:19,120
the road ahead is perilous.

165
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:22,200
Since you have difficulty walking,

166
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:24,064
I'll send you
to Imperial Palace.

167
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,559
Imperial Palace?

168
00:09:26,879 --> 00:09:28,360
Yeah, that's right.

169
00:09:29,399 --> 00:09:30,159
Be thankful.

170
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:35,879
You are

171
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:39,200
Duan Zhixing, Emperor of Dali?

172
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:39,799
Rude!

173
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:42,240
He's one of us.

174
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,919
I apologize, Gao Ang.

175
00:09:46,039 --> 00:09:48,720
I should've told you sooner.

176
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,679
Your Majesty, one more thing.

177
00:10:04,639 --> 00:10:05,039
Speak.

178
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,279
Yesterday,

179
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,600
I received news from Huan.

180
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,120
Consort Liu has

181
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,399
reached Mount Zhongnan.

182
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:14,759
Mount Zhongnan?

183
00:10:15,279 --> 00:10:15,720
Yes.

184
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:21,519
Gao Ang.

185
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:24,039
I send you back

186
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,759
because dangers await.

187
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,480
Probably

188
00:10:26,799 --> 00:10:28,639
even I may face peril.

189
00:10:32,639 --> 00:10:33,376
Your Majesty.

190
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:35,759
Why do you try

191
00:10:36,159 --> 00:10:37,120
to seek the Sutra?

192
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,840
You're not of the martial world.

193
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,679
So, you don't know how famous it is.

194
00:10:43,519 --> 00:10:44,919
Martial artists are eager for it.

195
00:10:45,159 --> 00:10:46,039
It's like

196
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:48,480
gourmands crave rare delicacies,

197
00:10:48,799 --> 00:10:49,559
or tea masters

198
00:10:49,919 --> 00:10:52,120
revere the tea art.

199
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,279
It's the supreme martial manual

200
00:10:54,679 --> 00:10:56,679
in the martial world,

201
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,440
containing mysteries

202
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:00,879
and profound wisdom.

203
00:11:02,519 --> 00:11:03,240
In my life,

204
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,279
if I could read it once,

205
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,159
I'd die without regrets.

206
00:11:09,039 --> 00:11:10,519
Then, having the Nine Yin True Sutra

207
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:12,679
will be

208
00:11:12,679 --> 00:11:13,720
your greatest pursuit.

209
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,159
Exactly.

210
00:11:17,799 --> 00:11:18,759
If you never find it?

211
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,399
Keep searching

212
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,159
until I find it.

213
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,000
And if you find it?

214
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,519
Well,

215
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:30,159
the Sutra's martial arts

216
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:32,039
are quite profound.

217
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,679
I'm afraid

218
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,440
I can't totally comprehend it

219
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:37,879
in my whole life.

220
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:52,600
Gao Ang.

221
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:53,960
Listen to me.

222
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:56,120
Return to the palace
and recover properly.

223
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:56,960
Then,

224
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:57,840
go back home

225
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,440
and build graves for your family.

226
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:03,080
At least, let their souls rest

227
00:12:03,159 --> 00:12:04,240
peacefully.

228
00:12:07,519 --> 00:12:08,279
Thank you.

229
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,399
I appreciate your kindness.

230
00:12:25,159 --> 00:12:25,720
I'd like

231
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:26,960
to toast you.

232
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:37,399
Okay.

233
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:47,840
Poison!

234
00:12:52,559 --> 00:12:53,120
Who are you?

235
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:54,679
Who sent you?

236
00:12:57,399 --> 00:12:58,279
Your Majesty.

237
00:12:58,679 --> 00:13:00,360
Who do you think sent me?

238
00:13:04,039 --> 00:13:05,360
You're so weak.

239
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:06,919
I don't think

240
00:13:06,919 --> 00:13:08,080
someone sent you to kill me.

241
00:13:08,679 --> 00:13:10,279
Dali's common people sent me.

242
00:13:11,039 --> 00:13:12,080
The soldiers sent me.

243
00:13:12,639 --> 00:13:13,919
The dead souls sent me.

244
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,559
You're raving mad!

245
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:18,000
Today's failed attempt

246
00:13:18,519 --> 00:13:19,960
shows my inferior skills.

247
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,720
But there are countless people like me

248
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:25,480
in Dongchuan,

249
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:27,600
Heyang,

250
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,240
Xiushan,

251
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,320
and Shicheng.

252
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:32,399
You escaped death today,

253
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,559
but not forever.

254
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:40,879
Tell me.

255
00:13:42,559 --> 00:13:43,679
Why do you hate me so much?

256
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:46,039
Why must you kill me?

257
00:13:48,159 --> 00:13:49,440
You're guilty.

258
00:13:49,519 --> 00:13:51,000
Absurd! I've been good to you.

259
00:13:51,279 --> 00:13:52,120
Why am I guilty?

260
00:13:54,559 --> 00:13:55,720
Listen up.

261
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:00,840
You committed three crimes.

262
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:03,960
First,

263
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:06,120
you claim you see your people
as your children.

264
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:09,720
So, Dali's people

265
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,120
are all like your children.

266
00:14:11,879 --> 00:14:15,840
Good parents love their children.

267
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:17,879
They care about their children.

268
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:21,159
They're concerned

269
00:14:21,279 --> 00:14:22,679
about their children.

270
00:14:23,679 --> 00:14:24,399
What about you?

271
00:14:25,759 --> 00:14:28,200
You let your children die in battle,

272
00:14:28,799 --> 00:14:30,080
rotting in fields.

273
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:31,879
You treat them as dust.

274
00:14:32,399 --> 00:14:33,960
You let them become beasts' food.

275
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:35,480
You tell me.

276
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,759
What kind of father are you?

277
00:14:39,679 --> 00:14:40,399
Second,

278
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:45,159
you're obsessed with martial arts,

279
00:14:45,879 --> 00:14:47,279
neglecting governance,

280
00:14:48,919 --> 00:14:50,919
and disgracing ancestral legacy.

281
00:14:51,279 --> 00:14:53,080
People get impoverished.

282
00:14:53,279 --> 00:14:54,480
The nation is in decline.

283
00:14:54,799 --> 00:14:56,000
Resentment grows.

284
00:14:56,679 --> 00:14:58,639
Your ancestors' legacy

285
00:14:58,960 --> 00:15:00,279
is crumbling in your hands.

286
00:15:00,679 --> 00:15:01,360
You tell me.

287
00:15:01,679 --> 00:15:03,000
What kind of ruler are you?

288
00:15:05,639 --> 00:15:06,879
Third,

289
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,559
you never knew

290
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:14,000
my deceased father and brother.

291
00:15:15,679 --> 00:15:17,600
Yet they knew you.

292
00:15:18,679 --> 00:15:20,448
In the autumn
of the fourth Jia Hui year,

293
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,639
a troop inspection in Dali.

294
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:26,360
You reviewed soldiers

295
00:15:26,879 --> 00:15:28,159
on the commander's platform.

296
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:31,279
To encourage them
to fight fearlessly in battle,

297
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:34,000
you promised

298
00:15:34,879 --> 00:15:37,840
you'd take care of their families.

299
00:15:39,399 --> 00:15:41,200
My father and brother

300
00:15:41,919 --> 00:15:42,919
