and receive your commendation.

307
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:07,200
Yet they both died in battle.

308
00:16:09,639 --> 00:16:10,120
But you

309
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:12,919
are so blind.

310
00:16:13,919 --> 00:16:16,600
The corrupt officials
embezzled compensation funds,

311
00:16:17,159 --> 00:16:20,120
disappointing countless dead souls.

312
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:23,960
My mother

313
00:16:24,919 --> 00:16:26,159
died from overwhelming grief

314
00:16:27,159 --> 00:16:28,360
the same year.

315
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:32,480
When I was hunted by corrupt officials,

316
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,759
my right foot was crushed by a horse,

317
