323
00:16:55,879 --> 00:16:57,039
You

324
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:59,480
search the martial world

325
00:16:59,759 --> 00:17:01,279
for the martial arts manual,

326
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:03,679
hoping to learn peerless skills

327
00:17:03,679 --> 00:17:04,759
