333
00:17:20,119 --> 00:17:20,839
You're right.

334
00:17:24,559 --> 00:17:25,519
I'm guilty.

335
00:17:27,279 --> 00:17:27,960
Even so,

336
00:17:29,759 --> 00:17:31,839
why did you take such extreme measures?

337
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:36,160
I am

338
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:38,119
crippled,

339
00:17:39,359 --> 00:17:40,759
but I have my pride.

340
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:43,480
The poisoned liquor was prepared

341
00:17:44,759 --> 00:17:45,519
for you

342
00:17:46,559 --> 00:17:47,440
and for me.

343
00:17:49,359 --> 00:17:50,799
I foresaw this outcome

344
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:52,559
