349
00:18:06,279 --> 00:18:07,720
I can die

350
00:18:08,359 --> 00:18:09,559
with no regrets.

351
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:19,680
Future generations cannot be deceived.

352
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:24,160
Whether you'll be eternally vilified

353
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:26,960
depends on your choice now.

354
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:30,920
Duan Zhixing.

355
00:18:32,519 --> 00:18:33,599
Emperor Duan.

356
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:36,240
Your Majesty.

357
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:41,200
Please

358
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:44,599
