359
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:09,759
Gao Ang.

360
00:19:12,400 --> 00:19:13,279
My brother.

361
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:16,160
May you rest in peace.

362
00:19:20,519 --> 00:19:25,920
Your words are etched in my mind.

363
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:31,000
I promise.

364
00:19:57,599 --> 00:19:58,519
I'll buy the info.

365
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:03,559
You're spending a fortune

366
00:20:03,559 --> 00:20:04,440
recklessly

367
00:20:04,440 --> 00:20:06,119
on the best martial arts manual.

368
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:07,519
No.

369
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:09,240
