No need for details.

379
00:20:25,799 --> 00:20:26,559
Give me the info.

380
00:20:26,880 --> 00:20:27,480
You'll be paid.

381
00:20:29,839 --> 00:20:30,880
Don't you

382
00:20:32,079 --> 00:20:33,200
seek the Sutra

383
