391
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:55,799
Mr. Duan, if you do it for yourself,

392
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:56,960
I will

393
00:20:58,119 --> 00:20:59,680
accept your gold.

394
00:21:00,680 --> 00:21:01,599
But if you do it

395
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:03,119
for your people,

396
00:21:03,519 --> 00:21:04,359
you don't

397
