have to pay.

398
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:09,960
Now,

399
00:21:10,519 --> 00:21:12,079
the Living Map of the Sutra

400
00:21:12,119 --> 00:21:13,240
is with Ouyang Feng,

401
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:15,279
on the road to Mount Zhongnan.

402
00:21:16,519 --> 00:21:17,079
Emperor Duan.

403
00:21:18,319 --> 00:21:18,960
Take care.

404
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:38,680
You all

405
00:21:40,079 --> 00:21:40,759
return to Dali.

406
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:42,920
