407
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:43,640
Await my words.

408
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:44,960
If

409
00:21:47,119 --> 00:21:48,680
I fail to obtain the Sutra,

410
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:51,559
I shall

411
00:21:52,839 --> 00:21:53,920
