434
00:23:08,839 --> 00:23:10,440
Evil men never do.

435
00:23:14,319 --> 00:23:14,920
Waiter.

436
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:19,720
Yes?

437
00:23:20,960 --> 00:23:21,759
How much

438
00:23:21,759 --> 00:23:22,640
