440
00:23:45,279 --> 00:23:46,240
My parents are dead.

441
00:23:46,839 --> 00:23:47,720
I've had my vengeance.

442
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:48,799
At worst,

443
00:23:48,799 --> 00:23:49,559
I'll die here.

444
00:23:50,559 --> 00:23:51,839
You're an evil guy.

445
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:53,200
If you get the Sutra,

446
00:23:53,359 --> 00:23:54,839
