458
00:25:09,839 --> 00:25:11,079
Apology accepted.

459
00:25:11,319 --> 00:25:11,960
Now, the girl.

460
00:25:12,240 --> 00:25:13,000
She can't leave.

461
00:25:14,039 --> 00:25:15,000
Haven't you been

462
00:25:15,000 --> 00:25:15,880
looking for the Sutra?

463
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:18,519
She's the Living Map of the Sutra.

464
00:25:26,559 --> 00:25:27,200
I see.

465
00:25:27,640 --> 00:25:28,480
What?

466
00:25:29,079 --> 00:25:30,519
A monarch like you

467
00:25:30,799 --> 00:25:32,079
also wants the Sutra?

468
00:25:32,759 --> 00:25:33,440
Give her to me.

469
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:35,519
Be it 10,000 taels of gold

470
00:25:35,759 --> 00:25:36,480
or 100 estates,

471
00:25:36,559 --> 00:25:37,680
name whatever I possess,

472
00:25:38,039 --> 00:25:38,680
and it's yours.

473
00:25:38,839 --> 00:25:40,119
What if I want your throne?

474
00:25:44,640 --> 00:25:45,400
My throne

475
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:48,839
is a cursed burden.

476
00:25:51,759 --> 00:25:53,240
A cursed burden.

477
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:54,680
Then stop wasting your breath.

478
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:55,640
Hand her over!

479
00:26:01,680 --> 00:26:02,440
Emperor Duan.

480
00:26:03,079 --> 00:26:05,200
What's the point
of having a dying person?

481
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:17,119
You poisoned her?

482
00:26:18,200 --> 00:26:19,480
She's the only living person

483
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,759
who knows the Sutra's location.

484
00:26:21,880 --> 00:26:23,240
Yet you poisoned her.

485
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:25,519
She swallowed the poison willingly.

486
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:28,000
But only I have the antidote.

487
00:26:30,319 --> 00:26:31,759
It's a poison from Mount Baituo.

488
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:33,240
She won't last long.

489
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:36,000
Let me see

490
00:26:36,119 --> 00:26:37,200
how you'll extract secrets

491
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:38,039
from a dead person

492
00:26:38,119 --> 00:26:39,799
to find the Nine Yin True Sutra.

493
00:26:43,599 --> 00:26:44,200
Liu Ying.

494
00:26:49,319 --> 00:26:49,880
Take her away.

495
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:51,920
Where to?

496
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:54,119
Just go!

497
00:26:57,640 --> 00:26:58,000
Let's go.

498
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:13,720
Ouyang.

499
00:28:14,640 --> 00:28:15,039
Sorry.

500
00:28:17,039 --> 00:28:18,160
I have my reason

501
00:28:18,440 --> 00:28:19,240
to get the Sutra.

502
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:21,640
Dali is in constant warfare.

503
00:28:22,599 --> 00:28:23,599
We lack strong troops.

504
00:28:24,200 --> 00:28:25,519
My people suffer from wars.

505
00:28:26,359 --> 00:28:27,720
I wish to master the Sutra

506
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:29,519
and teach my soldiers

507
00:28:30,079 --> 00:28:32,039
to enhance my military force

508
00:28:32,799 --> 00:28:33,839
and protect my people.

509
00:28:34,599 --> 00:28:35,920
You want the Sutra, don't you?

510
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:37,799
Stop cooking up a story.

511
00:28:38,279 --> 00:28:39,559
