518
00:28:51,880 --> 00:28:52,279
Wait!

519
00:28:55,519 --> 00:28:56,799
What martial art did you use?

520
00:29:00,279 --> 00:29:01,440
It's the signature technique,

521
00:29:02,359 --> 00:29:03,488
One-yang Finger.

522
00:29:19,359 --> 00:29:20,400
