533
00:29:40,480 --> 00:29:41,039
Try it.

534
00:29:50,480 --> 00:29:51,240
Can you guarantee

535
00:29:51,240 --> 00:29:52,480
that the Chongyang Temple

536
00:29:52,759 --> 00:29:54,119
