540
00:29:59,960 --> 00:30:01,119
One pill revives the dying.

541
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:02,720
This is our only hope now.

542
00:30:04,079 --> 00:30:05,279
Do you know Master Chongyang?

543
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:06,799
We've never met.

544
00:30:07,599 --> 00:30:09,359
But I hear he is righteous.

545
00:30:09,559 --> 00:30:10,680
I believe he will save her.

546
00:30:11,839 --> 00:30:12,279
Well,

547
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:13,440
