549
00:30:18,839 --> 00:30:19,279
My dear.

550
00:30:20,079 --> 00:30:21,319
You're a different woman.

551
00:30:22,119 --> 00:30:24,079
You love martial arts and have talent.

552
00:30:25,079 --> 00:30:26,200
