555
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,559
Since I've left the palace,

556
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:33,119
I won't go back.

557
00:30:35,119 --> 00:30:36,000
I wouldn't

558
00:30:36,799 --> 00:30:38,200
teach you point techniques

559
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:40,240
for a reason.

560
00:30:40,359 --> 00:30:41,440
What is it?

561
00:30:42,440 --> 00:30:43,799
The point techniques are

