565
00:30:47,440 --> 00:30:48,640
I can't teach outsiders.

566
00:30:49,240 --> 00:30:50,480
I took vows.

567
00:30:51,920 --> 00:30:52,519
To be honest,

568
00:30:52,920 --> 00:30:54,200
I yearn to pursue martial arts

569
00:30:55,880 --> 00:30:57,240
and roam the martial world freely.

570
00:30:58,519 --> 00:30:59,559
But the Imperial Palace is

571
00:31:00,599 --> 00:31:01,680
where an emperor stays.

572
00:31:02,359 --> 00:31:03,799
I have to act with caution

573
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,319
and weigh things out.

574
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:08,000
I can't behave unrestrained

575
00:31:08,119 --> 00:31:08,960
like a hero.

576
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:11,759
Ying.

577
00:31:13,279 --> 00:31:14,559
If you choose never to return,

578
00:31:15,519 --> 00:31:16,559
I won't stand in your way.

579
00:31:17,759 --> 00:31:19,559
But we are husband and wife.

580
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:21,200
So, one day,

581
00:31:22,759 --> 00:31:24,000
when you decide to return,

582
00:31:25,319 --> 00:31:27,680
