583
00:31:28,240 --> 00:31:29,559
in the palace.

584
00:31:31,240 --> 00:31:32,880
Are you truly content

585
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:34,559
to abandon the martial world

586
00:31:35,319 --> 00:31:36,160
and remain trapped

587
00:31:36,160 --> 00:31:37,079
in the Imperial Palace?

588
00:31:41,039 --> 00:31:42,200
Before coming here,

589
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:45,119
I encountered an orphan.

590
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:46,640
His entire family

591
00:31:47,799 --> 00:31:48,720
had perished.

592
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:49,880
He fled

593
00:31:50,799 --> 00:31:51,839
to the Song,

594
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:54,839
enduring hardships and humiliations.

595
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:57,279
He attempted to kill me,

596
00:31:58,119 --> 00:31:58,839
